{"tid":2264990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"安心出行APP 讓市民記錄行蹤 政府260場地試行健康碼1.0","createTime":"2020-10-31T05:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T11:44:03.000Z","uid":198957,"like":3,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5b786cf819bed3fa522874d7a6ed0d7ac64189","tid":2264990,"uid":198957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"該流動應用程式名為「安心出行」，與目前已在內地廣泛實施的「健康碼」類似，惟市民可自行選擇是否下載應用程式，用戶到訪場所時可掃瞄場地展示的二維碼，應用程式會在用戶的手機紀錄到訪過的地點。如場所出現確診個案，流動程式會向用戶發出通知，若用戶確診，衞生防護中心會聯絡用戶提供出行記錄，協助追尋相關接觸者。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n政府聲稱，用戶的資料不會上傳到任何中央資料庫。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/YUKGBL3J5NHOJPQVBJP4CKD3KA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FYUKGBL3J5NHOJPQVBJP4CKD3KA%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=2596312b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FYUKGBL3J5NHOJPQVBJP4CKD3KA%2F&h=f59a7f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/YUKGBL3J5NHOJPQVBJP4CKD3KA/</a>"},{"pid":"81a6df82b564a99d92c0266e8d4e5261cbf577f9","tid":2264990,"uid":137493,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a754010fd27a3f66b165ddcbcc6a5f7f2eb305fe","tid":2264990,"uid":142574,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"不會上傳到任何中央資料庫, 甘仲有咩作用"},{"pid":"e164782021e2fdc10dcd33f665ad8f810e338208","tid":2264990,"uid":198957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"香港離新疆不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305be800a0a4b0e58989889f84542a9571aac9f0","tid":2264990,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"會每去港共資料庫<br 